OL,3,CMeet Boris: The 60-year-old tortoise
OL,4,Cwith a Lego wheel prosthetic
OL,6,FMeet Boris, the 60-year-old tortoise
OL,7,Fwith a unique tale to tell.
OL,9,FA few years ago, Boris had to have his
OL,10,Fback leg amputated at the vets after
OL,11,Fgetting gout.
OL,13,FHe has now been nursed back to full
OL,14,Ffitness by his owner, with a little
OL,15,Fhelp from a nifty bit of imagination -
OL,16,Fhis back leg was replaced by a Lego
OL,17,Fwheel so he could keep moving.
