OL,3,CMeet Boris: The 60-year-old tortoise
OL,4,Cwith a Lego wheel prosthetic
OL,6,FCollette Sloan, who adopted Boris from
OL,7,Fa local tortoise sanctuary after
OL,8,Fhaving his foot amputated, told ITV
OL,9,FNews: "He'd lost his leg and was just
OL,10,Fhad his wheel fitted when I took him
OL,11,Fon, so I still did a bit of nursing
OL,12,Fwith him but he did get his wheel off
OL,13,Fseveral times so we had to keep taking
OL,14,Fhim back to the vet but we've sorted
OL,15,Fthat out now.
OL,17,F"We tend to keep it on for a good year
OL,18,For two."
