OL,3,CMeet Boris: The 60-year-old tortoise
OL,4,Cwith a Lego wheel prosthetic
OL,6,FWhen asked why a Lego wheel was the
OL,7,Fperfect fit for Boris, Collette said:
OL,8,F"The size was just right; he just
OL,9,Fneeded something very little.
OL,11,F"When he first had it on he used it
OL,12,Flike a crutch and he sort of hopped
OL,13,Falong on it. He wasn't quite sure what
OL,14,Fto do with this alien piece of
OL,15,Fequipment.
OL,17,F"But slowly he just learned to use his
OL,18,Fthree legs and just wheel the wheel
OL,19,Falong as though it were a leg. I mean,
OL,20,Fhe's adapted fantastically and he gets
OL,21,Faround really well with it.
