OL,3,CMeet Boris: The 60-year-old tortoise
OL,4,Cwith a Lego wheel prosthetic
OL,6,F"He can get round quite fast when he
OL,7,Fwants to."
OL,9,FCollette has a track record for
OL,10,Flooking after pets with disabilities.
OL,12,FShe also has an 18-year-old cat, Daffy
OL,13,Fwho is deaf and has advanced dementia.
OL,15,FCollette said: "My little cat, she's
OL,16,F18 now. A little bit deaf and has
OL,17,Fsenile dementia but she fits in well
OL,18,Fwith the family!"
